0. product-list.html ni togrilash ✅
1. static(css, js, images) fayllarni togrilash ✅
2. asosiy papkani rootga ozgartirish ✅
3. base.html ajratish ✅
4. modellarni yozish
productni kop rasmli qilish, productni description fieldiga ckeditor ishlatish
product da discount(chegirma %)
product da author bolishi kk
quantity (bazadagi mahsulotni soni)

category ni mptt dan foydalanish ✅
tag ham qoshish kk ✅
5. postgres db ulash kk
ozimizni ismimiz bilan user ochib, root nomli db ochamiz paroli 1 bolsin✅

6. product listda NEW nomli badge chiqsin agar tovar qoshilganga 7kundan oshmagan bolsa
7. login(email, password), register(pochtaga verification link yuboramiz + celery qoshish kk (brokerga rabbitmq))
8. settings.html togrilash, rasm va malumotlarni update qiladigan qilish
9. rasmlarni minioda saqlidigan qilamiz
10. product listda pagination qilish
11. add to cart product detail dagi bosganda shopping-cart.html shopping cart ga qoshish kk
12. modellarni yozish (Order, OrderItem, Cart) ✅
13. region, district va country ni fixtures qilib qoshish kk va makefilega cmd qoshish kk
14.. userga phone qoshish (login da phone orqali yoki email orqali)
15. telegram orqali kirish
16. README.md faylga saytda ishlatilgan texnologiyalarni yozib va
saytda nimalar borligini yozib screenshot qilib qoyamiz, github ga yuklanadi
17. ckeditorni file storage ni minio ga qaratish kk
18. register qismida, phone bolsa, 1minutlik[cache ga expire qilib saqlanadi] 6xonali kod yuboradi(ekranga print qilinadi) 7-taskga qarang
19. adminkada product list page da, productga tegishli imagelar soni va oxirida
20. category ni 3talik ichma ich qilish va category ga icon qoshish kk (icon code yoki icon ozi[rasm holatda])
21. adminkada product list displayda category nomini ustiga bosganda shu category product larni chiqarishi kk


python,django,celery,postgresql


